KW  - Investor disagreement
KW  - Social media
KW  - Divergence of opinion
KW  - Convergence of opinion
KW  - Trading volume
KW  - Stock returns
KW  - Earnings announcement
AB  - We collect a unique dataset of Twitter posts to examine the change in investor disagreement around earnings announcements. We find that investors' opinions can either converge (reduced disagreement) or diverge (increased disagreement) around earnings announcements. The convergence and divergence of opinion has significant effects on trading volume and return. Consistent with theoretical predictions, both the convergence and divergence of opinion are associated with a greater volume reaction to earnings news. While the convergence of opinion is associated with lower earnings announcement returns, the divergence of opinion is associated with higher earnings announcement returns.
ER  - 
